'''崔佛·約翰·史托瑞'''（{{lang-en|Trevor John Story}}，{{bd|1992年|11月15日}}）是一位[[美國|美國]][[職業棒球|職業棒球]][[游擊手|游擊手]]，目前效力於波士頓紅襪，他先前曾效力過科羅拉多洛磯。2016年4月4日，他初次登場大聯盟。2016年4月8日，史托瑞成為大聯盟首位在職業生涯前四場比賽皆擊出[[全壘打|全壘打]]的菜鳥球員。

==早年生涯==
史托瑞曾在[[德克薩斯州|德克薩斯州]][[歐文_(德克薩斯州)|歐文]]的{{le|歐文高中|Irving High School}}就讀。他在該校的棒球隊中擔任[[游擊手|游擊手]]及[[投手|投手]]，他的[[快速球|快速球]]球速更高達{{convert|96|mph}}。<ref name=goodkid/>他也曾打過[[美式足球|美式足球]]，場上位置為[[四分衛|四分衛]]，但他到了高中二年級時便不再打美式足球，因此能更加專注於棒球。<ref name=firstchapter>{{cite web|url=http://blogs.denverpost.com/rockies/2011/09/19/rockies-trevor-story-writes-first-chapter-in-casper/9651/|title=Rockies' Trevor Story writes first chapter in Casper|work=On the Rox|accessdate=2016-04-05|archive-date=2016-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160417064736/http://blogs.denverpost.com/rockies/2011/09/19/rockies-trevor-story-writes-first-chapter-in-casper/9651/|dead-url=no}}</ref>之後，他獲得[[路易斯安那州立大學|路易斯安那州立大學]]（LSU）提供的{{le|大學棒球|college baseball}}獎學金。<ref name=goodkid>{{cite web|url=http://www.dallasnews.com/news/community-news/coppell/headlines/20101031-Good-Kid-Meet-Trevor-Story-1084.ece|title=Good Kid: Meet Trevor Story of Irving High|work=Dallas Morning News|accessdate=2016-04-05|archive-date=2016-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160417085001/http://www.dallasnews.com/news/community-news/coppell/headlines/20101031-Good-Kid-Meet-Trevor-Story-1084.ece|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://sportsday.dallasnews.com/high-school/highschoolheadlines/2011/05/04/meet-irving_s-trevor-story-the-shortstop-who-attracted-28-scouts-to-a-practice-this-season|title=Meet Irving's Trevor Story: The shortstop who attracted 28 scouts to a practice this season|work=Dallas Morning News|date=2011-05-04|accessdate=2016-04-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160414114750/http://sportsday.dallasnews.com/high-school/highschoolheadlines/2011/05/04/meet-irving_s-trevor-story-the-shortstop-who-attracted-28-scouts-to-a-practice-this-season|archive-date=2016-04-14|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

==職業生涯==
===小聯盟===
史托瑞在[[2011年美國職棒大聯盟選秀|2011年美國職棒大聯盟選秀]]被[[科羅拉多落磯|科羅拉多落磯]]以第1輪（第45名）的順位選中。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://m.mlb.com/col/video/topic/8877456/v15620111/draft-2011-story-goes-to-rockies-with-45th-pick|title=The Rockies draft Story No. 45|work=MLB.com|format=video|accessdate=2016-04-05|archive-date=2016-04-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160418104541/http://m.mlb.com/col/video/topic/8877456/v15620111/draft-2011-story-goes-to-rockies-with-45th-pick|dead-url=no}}</ref>史托瑞放棄進入LSU就讀，而是選擇與洛磯簽約，並獲得915,000元[[美金|美金]]的[[簽約獎金|簽約獎金]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.courant.com/sports/baseball/hc-rock-cats-trevor-story-0507-20150506-story.html|title=Trevor Story Tearing It Up With The Bat For Rock Cats|author=Hartford Courant|date=2015-05-06|work=courant.com|accessdate=2016-04-05|archive-date=2019-12-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191207111451/https://www.courant.com/sports/baseball/hc-rock-cats-trevor-story-0507-20150506-story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sportingnews.com/mlb-news/4700870-who-is-trevor-story-home-run-zack-greinke-rockies-debut-opening-day-fantasy|title=Introducing Trevor Story: Rockies SS takes Zack Greinke deep twice in debut|first=Tom|last=Gatto|work=Sporting News|accessdate=2016-04-05|archive-date=2016-04-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160419003533/http://www.sportingnews.com/mlb-news/4700870-who-is-trevor-story-home-run-zack-greinke-rockies-debut-opening-day-fantasy|dead-url=no}}</ref>簽約後，他效力於[[美國職棒小聯盟#新人聯盟（Class_Rookie）|新人級]]{{le|先鋒聯盟 (棒球)|Pioneer League (baseball)|先鋒聯盟}}的{{le|卡斯伯幽靈|Casper Ghosts}}，繳出[[打擊率|打擊率]]0.268的成績。<ref name=firstchapter/>史托瑞在2012年上升至[[美國職棒小聯盟#1A（Class_A）|1A]]{{le|南大西洋聯盟|South Atlantic League}}（SAL）的{{le|艾許威爾旅行者|Asheville Tourists}}，以打擊率0.277及18支[[全壘打|全壘打]]的成績，獲選為SAL季後賽全明星陣容。<ref name=asfg>{{cite web|url=http://www.milb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20150625&content_id=132904290&fext=.jsp&vkey=news_t573|title=Former Tourists Story And Tapia Selected To MLB Futures Game; Ocasio Named A Coach To The World Team - MiLB.com News - The Official Site of Minor League Baseball|work=MiLB.com|accessdate=2016-04-05|archive-date=2016-04-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160418171540/http://www.milb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20150625&content_id=132904290&fext=.jsp&vkey=news_t573|dead-url=no}}</ref>2013年賽季前，史托瑞在[[MLB.com|MLB.com]]的最受看好新秀排名中位在第99名。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://colorado.rockies.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20130129&content_id=41242248&vkey=news_col&c_id=col |title=Rockies place three on Top 100 Prospects list |work=MLB.com |date=2013-01-29 |accessdate=2013-06-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130131082421/http://colorado.rockies.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20130129&content_id=41242248&vkey=news_col&c_id=col |archive-date=2013-01-31 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>史托瑞在2013年效力於[[美國職棒小聯盟#高階1A（Class_A_Advanced）|高階1A]]{{le|加利福尼亞聯盟|California League}}的[[莫德斯托樫果|莫德斯托樫果]]，不過他的表現低迷，打擊率僅有0.233。<ref name=chapter/>在2014年繼續效力莫德斯托並繳出打擊率0.332的成績後，落磯於6月將史托瑞上升至[[美國職棒小聯盟#2A（Class_AA）|2A]]{{le|德克薩斯聯盟|Texas League}}的{{le|土桑鑽孔機|Tulsa Drillers}}。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.tulsaworld.com/blogs/sports/probaseball/pro-baseball-top-rockies-infield-prospect-joins-drillers/article_6da732c2-18be-5f21-8ad7-6ab225515d5c.html|title=Pro baseball: Top Rockies infield prospect joins Drillers|work=Tulsa World|accessdate=2016-04-05|archive-date=2019-12-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191207055900/https://www.tulsaworld.com/blogs/sports/probaseball/pro-baseball-top-rockies-infield-prospect-joins-drillers/article_6da732c2-18be-5f21-8ad7-6ab225515d5c.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>不過，他在土桑的表現不佳，打擊率僅有0.205。<ref name=chapter/>

因為[[特洛伊·托洛維斯基|特洛伊·托洛維斯基]]佔據了洛磯隊的游擊手位置，史托瑞開始累積[[二壘手|二壘手]]及[[三壘手|三壘手]]的經驗。<ref name=roadblock/>2015年賽季開始，他效力於2A[[東方聯盟|東方聯盟]]的{{le|新不列顛石貓|New Britain Rock Cats}}，在300次[[打席|打席]]中繳出打擊率0.281的成績，並在7月1日上升至[[美國職棒小聯盟#3A（Class_AAA）|3A]][[太平洋岸聯盟|太平洋岸聯盟]]的{{le|愛伯克奇同位素|Albuquerque Isotopes}}。<ref name=roadblock/><ref name=chapter>{{cite web|url=http://www.denverpost.com/rockies/ci_28725957/story-near-big-league-chapter|title=Rockies shortstop prospect Trevor Story near big-league chapter|author=Patrick Saunders|work=The Denver Post|date=2015-08-30|accessdate=2016-04-05|archive-date=2016-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160417030105/http://www.denverpost.com/rockies/ci_28725957/story-near-big-league-chapter|dead-url=no}}</ref>2015年賽季期間，洛磯將托洛維斯基交易出去，<ref name=history>{{cite web|url=http://www.milb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20160405&content_id=170536234&fext=.jsp&vkey=news_milb&sid=milb|title=Colorado Rockies' Trevor Story blasts way into the history books - MiLB.com News - The Official Site of Minor League Baseball|work=MiLB.com|accessdate=2016-04-05|archive-date=2016-08-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160808005551/http://www.milb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20160405&content_id=170536234&fext=.jsp&vkey=news_milb&sid=milb|dead-url=no}}</ref>史托瑞也入選{{le|未來之星明星賽|All-Star Futures Game}}。<ref name=asfg/><ref name=roadblock>{{cite web|url=http://sportsday.dallasnews.com/high-school/highschoolheadlines/2015/07/30/rockies-trade-of-troy-tulowitzki-clears-roadblock-cleared-for-irving-s-story|title=Rockies' trade of Troy Tulowitzki clears roadblock cleared for Irving's Story|work=Dallas Morning News|accessdate=2016-04-05|archive-date=2019-04-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190401140341/https://sportsday.dallasnews.com/high-school/highschoolheadlines/2015/07/30/rockies-trade-of-troy-tulowitzki-clears-roadblock-cleared-for-irving-s-story|dead-url=no}}</ref>他在2015年賽季效力新不列顛與愛伯克奇期間，共繳出[[上壘率|上壘率]]0.350及20支全壘打的成績。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/sports/mlb/2016/03/30/trevor-storys-time-arrives-quickly-rockies/82452020/|title=Trevor Story's time arrives quickly with Rockies|date=2016-03-30|work=USA TODAY|accessdate=2016-04-05|archive-date=2019-12-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191207112755/https://www.usatoday.com/story/sports/mlb/2016/03/30/trevor-storys-time-arrives-quickly-rockies/82452020/|dead-url=no}}</ref>洛磯在2015年賽季結束後，將史托瑞放進40人名單。<ref name="mlb.com">{{cite web|url=http://m.rockies.mlb.com/news/article/157821672/rockies-john-axford-designated-for-assignment|title=Rockies' John Axford designated for assignment|work=MLB.com|accessdate=2016-02-04|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304125731/http://m.rockies.mlb.com/news/article/157821672/rockies-john-axford-designated-for-assignment|dead-url=no}}</ref>

===科羅拉多洛磯===
史托瑞在2016年{{le|春訓|Spring training}}期間，與{{le|克里斯蒂安·亞當斯|Cristhian Adames}}角逐洛磯的先發游擊手位置。他在春訓期間繳出打擊率0.340，使他被排進了洛磯的{{le|開幕戰|Opening Day}}陣容。<ref name=history/> 

2016年4月4日，史托瑞在開幕戰對上[[亞利桑那響尾蛇|亞利桑那響尾蛇]]當日，以洛磯先發游擊手之姿初登大聯盟。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.denverpost.com/kiszla/ci_29720968/kiszla-rookie-story-breathes-life-into-opening-day|title=Rookie Trevor Story breathes life into opening day|work=Denver Post|first=Mark|last=Kiszla|date=2016-04-04|accessdate=2016-04-04|archive-date=2016-05-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160510004411/http://www.denverpost.com/kiszla/ci_29720968/kiszla-rookie-story-breathes-life-into-opening-day|dead-url=no}}</ref>史托瑞在他的大聯盟第二個[[打數|打數]]，便從[[扎克·格林基|扎克·格林基]]手中擊出他的生涯首支安打——一支三分全壘打。接著，他在下一次打席再度從格林基手中敲出全壘打。他是目前第七位能夠在對上格林基時，單場擊出雙響砲的球員，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://espn.go.com/mlb/playbyplay?gameId=360404129|title=Colorado Rockies vs. Arizona Diamondbacks - Play By Play - April 04, 2016|website=ESPN.com|accessdate=2016-04-04|archive-date=2016-06-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160619220304/http://espn.go.com/mlb/playbyplay?gameId=360404129|dead-url=no}}</ref>也成為了大聯盟史上繼{{le|查理·萊利|Charlie Reilly}}、{{le|鮑勃·尼曼|Bob Nieman}}、[[伯特·坎潘奈瑞斯|伯特·坎潘奈瑞斯]]、{{le|馬克·奎因|Mark Quinn}}及{{le|J·P·艾倫西比亞|J. P. Arencibia}}後，第六位在初登場時敲出雙響砲的的球員。在這六位球員當中，史托瑞又屬唯一一位在開幕戰初登場的球員。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://espn.go.com/espn/elias?date=20160405|title=Elias Says...|work=ESPN.com|date=2016-04-05|accessdate=2016-04-05|archive-date=2016-04-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160415015041/http://espn.go.com/espn/elias?date=20160405|dead-url=no}}</ref>隔日，他成為繼萊利及{{le|喬·坎寧安|Joe Cunningham}}後，第三位在生涯前兩場比賽敲出三支全壘打的球員。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://espn.go.com/espn/elias?date=20160406|title=Elias Says...|work=ESPN.com|date=2016-04-06|accessdate=2016-04-06|archive-date=2016-04-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160415160611/http://espn.go.com/espn/elias?date=20160406|dead-url=no}}</ref>在史托瑞站上大聯盟的第三天，他從響尾蛇的{{le|派崔克·寇賓|Patrick Corbin}}手中敲出一支兩分砲，使他成為大聯盟史上首位在生涯前三場比賽皆擊出全壘打，以及在生涯前四支安打皆為全壘打的球員。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://espn.go.com/mlb/recap?gameId=360406129|title=Amazing Story: rookie makes history with another HR|author=Associated Press|publisher=ESPN|date=2016-04-06|accessdate=2016-04-07|archive-date=2016-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160701062635/http://espn.go.com/mlb/recap?gameId=360406129|dead-url=no}}</ref>

在他的第四場比賽當中，他從[[聖地牙哥教士|聖地牙哥教士]]的手中擊出雙響砲，成為首位在生涯前四場比賽皆敲出全壘打的菜鳥球員，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://espn.go.com/mlb/story/_/id//trevor-story-colorado-rockies-first-player-homer-first-four-games|title=Rockies' Trevor Story first rookie ever to homer in first four games|work=ESPN.com|date=2016-04-08|accessdate=2016-04-08}}</ref>以及大聯盟歷史上首位在開季前四場比賽敲出六支全壘打的球員。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://espn.go.com/espn/elias?date=20160409|title=Elias Says: Story gets better every day|work=Elias Sports Bureau|publisher=ESPN|date=2016-04-09|accessdate=2016-04-10|archive-date=2016-04-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160418092909/http://espn.go.com/espn/elias?date=20160409|dead-url=no}}</ref>他未能在同樣對上教士的生涯第五場比賽當中擊出全壘打，不過，到了第六場比賽，順利從{{le|布蘭登·毛雷爾|Brandon Maurer}}手中敲出一支全壘打。<ref name=caps>{{cite web|url=http://espn.go.com/mlb/recap?gameId=360410127|title=Trevor Story caps first week with MLB-record 7th HR as Rockies win|work=ESPN|date=2016-04-11|accessdate=2016-04-11|archive-date=2016-07-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160717000838/http://espn.go.com/mlb/recap?gameId=360410127|dead-url=no}}</ref>為此，他寫下在球隊前六場比賽擊出最多支全壘打（7支）的MLB紀錄，改寫原先由[[賴瑞·沃克|賴瑞·沃克]]、[[麥克·施密特|麥克·施密特]]及[[威利·梅斯|威利·梅斯]]創下的六場比賽六支全壘打的紀錄。<ref name=caps/>史托瑞贏得了本賽季首週的{{le|美國職棒大聯盟當週最佳球員獎|Major League Baseball Player of the Week Award|國家聯盟當週最佳球員獎}}。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.denverpost.com/rockies/ci_29752716/trevor-story-named-nl-player-week|title=Rockies rookie Trevor Story named NL player of the week: Rookie Tyler White wins AL honor|work=The Denver Post|date=2016-04-11|accessdate=2016-04-11|archive-date=2016-05-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160515003439/http://www.denverpost.com/rockies/ci_29752716/trevor-story-named-nl-player-week|dead-url=no}}</ref>

